<lb ed="I" n="0158a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>靜明等修塔造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0158a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陰</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陰</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0158a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0158a0101">蓋玄宗凝湛。至道沖<note n="0158001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30933"/>＝煥【史】</note><note n="0158001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30933"/>【佛拓】，煥【史】</note><app n="0158001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">煥</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30933"/></rdg></app>。既
<lb ed="I" n="0158a02" type="honorific"/>幽且<note n="0158002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30835"/>＝遠【史】</note><note n="0158002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30835"/>【佛拓】，遠【史】</note><app n="0158002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30835"/></rdg></app>。似滅如存。雖復天
<lb ed="I" n="0158a03" type="honorific"/><note n="0158003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30934"/>＝旋【史】</note><note n="0158003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30934"/>【佛拓】，旋【史】</note><app n="0158003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旋</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30934"/></rdg></app>地遊。不究空<note n="0158004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡧘＝寂【史】</note><note n="0158004" resp="ihp" type="mod">𡧘【佛拓】，寂【史】</note><app n="0158004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡧘</rdg></app>之境。日
<lb ed="I" n="0158a04" type="honorific"/>住月來。詎盡微妙之域。至
<lb ed="I" n="0158a05" type="honorific"/>於出入四生。迴<note n="0158005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30935"/>＝還【史】</note><note n="0158005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30935"/>【佛拓】，還【史】</note><app n="0158005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">還</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30935"/></rdg></app>六道。<note n="0158a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0158a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0158a06" type="honorific"/>不<note n="0158006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30936"/>＝顧【史】</note><note n="0158006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30936"/>【佛拓】，顧【史】</note><app n="0158006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顧</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30936"/></rdg></app>己愛身。視陰昔日。智
<lb ed="I" n="0158a07" type="honorific"/>惠莫之留。神力不能保。而
<lb ed="I" n="0158a08" type="honorific"/>大慈應世。法輪既轉。群生
<lb ed="I" n="0158a09" type="honorific"/>於是迴向。庶類所以歸依。
<lb ed="I" n="0158a10" type="honorific"/>智禪師弟子靜明。知生生
<lb ed="I" n="0158a11" type="honorific"/>之非有覺滅滅之為空。思
<lb ed="I" n="0158a12" type="honorific"/>運己於法<note n="0158007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">舩＝船【史】</note><note n="0158007" resp="ihp" type="mod">舩【佛拓】，船【史】</note><app n="0158007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">船</lem><rdg wit="【原】">舩</rdg></app>。欲<note n="0158008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30937"/>＝澡【史】</note><note n="0158008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30937"/>【佛拓】，澡【史】</note><app n="0158008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">澡</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30937"/></rdg></app>心於正
<lb ed="I" n="0158a13" type="honorific"/>水。以大齊天保八年歲次
<lb ed="I" n="0158a14" type="honorific"/>丁丑十一月廿九日。<note n="0158009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">勧＝勸【史】</note><note n="0158009" resp="ihp" type="mod">勧【佛拓】，勸【史】</note><app n="0158009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">勧</rdg></app>化
<lb ed="I" n="0158a15" type="honorific"/>邑義等。脩孫<note n="0158010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㟵＝崗【史】</note><note n="0158010" resp="ihp" type="mod">㟵【佛拓】，崗【史】</note><app n="0158010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">崗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㟵</rdg></app>上故塔并
<lb ed="I" n="0158a16" type="honorific"/>石象一區。嵩山帶其左。神
<lb ed="I" n="0158a17" type="honorific"/>堆挾其右。南<note n="0158011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30940"/>＝望【史】</note><note n="0158011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30940"/>【佛拓】，望【史】</note><app n="0158011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30940"/></rdg></app>脩嶺。北眺
<lb ed="I" n="0158a18" type="honorific"/>萇河。擢茲勝地。建此良因。
<lb ed="I" n="0158a19" type="honorific"/>於是名僧慕義。上德依仁。
<lb ed="I" n="0158a20" type="honorific"/>庶以此福。普及群生。使國
<lb ed="I" n="0158a21" type="honorific"/>祚大康。世業永固。合邑諸
<lb ed="I" n="0158a22" type="honorific"/>人。俱昇寶舟。同濟彼岸。年
<lb ed="I" n="0158a23" type="honorific"/>住如流。時事焉屬。唯刊与
<lb ed="I" n="0158a24" type="honorific"/>石。永為不朽。　其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0158a25" type="honorific"/>神宗無極。空<app type="star" corresp="#0158004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡧘</rdg></app>難元。唯見
<lb ed="I" n="0158a26" type="honorific"/>生滅。交互相翻。仁師<app type="star" corresp="#0158002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30835"/></rdg></app>識。
<lb ed="I" n="0158a27" type="honorific"/>建此良因。東西勸化。邑義
<lb ed="I" n="0158a28" type="honorific"/>同津。脩營故塔。宛麗初新。
<lb ed="I" n="0158a29" type="honorific"/>寶舟共汎。捨偽歸真。</p>
</cb:div>
